{
  "stem": "802.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, all our friends were there and some of our relatives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was singing during the wedding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It was very informal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I-- I used to paint as a child, so I became a fashion illustrator later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But after Fern was born, I-- and then actually, after Stephanie was born, too, I decided when I was 30 years old, that my you know, life was slipping through my fingers, as it was.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I wasn't doing anything that was of any significance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I began to take-- actually, before that, I began to take courses at the New School for Social Research-- courses in philosophy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from there, I decided-- when we moved here, actually, I decided to go to college, which was extremely difficult, because I had nothing to show that I had ever gone to school.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You needed to show something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My sister did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She lived in Cleveland at the time, and she was working with a teacher in school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she-- and my sister has a wonderful way with children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So this-- her teacher urged her to go to college.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So she just went to either the college president-- it was Western--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and-- and he accepted her without anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she has an-- an MA in reading.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anyway, so then I decided to go to college.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took the GRE exam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I prepared myself, obviously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went into a special program.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's called the Special Baccalaureate Degree Program at Brooklyn College, from which I graduated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm going to both-- Phi Beta Kappa, magna cum laude, and Alpha Sigma Lambda, which was another, you know, honor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after I stopped-- after I graduated, I began teaching at Brooklyn College.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then-- and I, of course, continued my studies.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
